But what happened
at the school a year ago?

385
00:24:22,794 --> 00:24:24,462
Ask Eun-byeol's mom.

386
00:24:24,629 --> 00:24:27,048
Didn't you say
Eun-byeol and Su-in were close?

387
00:24:28,967 --> 00:24:32,429
