392
00:24:53,450 --> 00:24:54,701
It's nothing.

393
00:24:56,453 --> 00:24:57,537
Give me that.

394
00:24:59,789 --> 00:25:01,166
Did something bad happen?

395
00:25:01,708 --> 00:25:04,294
