-We're here!
-It's Tongyeong!

406
00:25:50,966 --> 00:25:52,634
Ra-jin, that's enough.

407
00:25:52,884 --> 00:25:53,969
I'm fine.

408
00:25:59,516 --> 00:26:00,725
